CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 20, 1954, pg. 26 reads: "Classy Five - The five lads shown above are favored to win the YMCA basketball tournament which begins at the Centre Avenue YMCA Friday. The team, billed as the All Stars, are, left to right: Bobby Jones, George Brown, Gerald Averytt, Donald Feabry and Ellsworth Morgan.  Morgan is home form Yale where he starred on their basketball team during the past season. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Bobby Jones, George Brown, Gerald Averytt, Donald Feabry and Ellsworth Morgan, standing around table with trophy in Centre Avenue YMCA
